  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个CodeIgniter框架的请求处理流程图，从浏览器发请求开始，到最终响应返回。我想先确认整体结构：首先是HTTP请求进来，然后经过Public目录下的index.php入口文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP Request Received",
        "Public Index.php"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，入口文件是public/index.php对吧？我注意到您说的是CodeIgniter，这是PHP框架，所以引导流程应该是先加载框架核心。我画的时候把入口文件指向框架引导步骤，这样逻辑顺吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Public Index.php",
        "CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，顺序没错。index.php里面主要是定义路径常量、加载Autoloader，然后启动CodeIgniter核心。接下来关键一步是Routing，要根据URL确定调用哪个Controller的哪个方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework",
        "Routing Determines Controller and Method"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把框架引导和路由判断这两个节点加上。路由节点我标注为\"Routing Determines Controller and Method\"，强调它同时解析控制器类名和具体方法名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Routing Determines Controller and Method"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "路由确定之后，框架会实例化对应的Controller。这里要注意，CodeIgniter的控制器是通过依赖注入容器来创建的，所以我在图上想体现\"Controller Instantiated\"这个明确的步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller Instantiated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "实例化之后，控制器需要加载业务依赖对吧？我想到CodeIgniter可以在构造函数里加载Model，也可以用到的时候再加载。您希望图上体现哪种方式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller Instantiated",
        "Controller Loads Models and Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "统一放在\"Controller Loads Models and Services\"这一步吧，这样流程清晰。实际项目中可能是懒加载，但流程图里合并展示更直观。加载完依赖，控制器就开始处理具体的业务逻辑了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller Loads Models and Services",
        "Controller Processes Request Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。业务逻辑处理完，下一步应该是准备视图数据？我记得CodeIgniter传统用法是把数据数组传给视图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller Processes Request Logic",
        "Prepare Data Array for View"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，但有个细节：我们项目用的是Mustache模板引擎，不是CodeIgniter原生的视图解析器。所以最后渲染那一步要特别强调一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Prepare Data Array for View",
        "Render View via Mustache Engine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，Mustache是逻辑less的模板引擎，和CodeIgniter原生视图不同。我把渲染节点写成\"Render View via Mustache Engine\"，最后一步就是HTTP响应返回浏览器，这样整个闭环就完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Render View via Mustache Engine",
        "Send Final Response to Browser"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整体流程对了，但我刚注意到一个问题：CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework这个节点，您写的是\"framew\"还是\"framework\"？缩写容易造成歧义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我检查了一下确实写成了\"framew\"，是不完整的。我修正为完整的\"CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework\"，保证术语准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "还有Routing那个节点，我想确认下表述：是\"Determines Controller and Method\"还是只写\"Determines Controller\"？因为有些框架路由只到控制器层面，方法是通过约定或反射找的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Routing Determines Controller and Method"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我确认写的是\"Controller and Method\"，因为CodeIgniter的路由确实要明确到方法，比如Welcome::index这种格式。如果只写Controller会丢失关键信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Routing Determines Controller and Method"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那没问题。另外我想在Controller Processes Request Logic之后加个判断分支的想法——不过算了，保持线性流程吧，这个图主要是给新人理解主链路用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller Processes Request Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解，主流程图保持线性更清晰。我现在把整个链条串一遍：HTTP请求→Public Index.php→框架引导→路由解析→控制器实例化→加载模型服务→处理业务逻辑→准备视图数据→Mustache渲染→返回浏览器。一共10个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP Request Received",
        "Public Index.php",
        "CodeIgniter Bootstraps Framework",
        "Routing Determines Controller and Method",
        "Controller Instantiated",
        "Controller Loads Models and Services",
        "Controller Processes Request Logic",
        "Prepare Data Array for View",
        "Render View via Mustache Engine",
        "Send Final Response to Browser"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "节点数量合适。不过Prepare Data Array for View这个表述，\"Array\"是不是太PHP-specific了？其他语言背景的同事可能不太理解。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Prepare Data Array for View"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确实，但既然整个图都是CodeIgniter/PHP语境，保持\"Data Array\"反而更准确，因为Mustache在PHP里接收的就是关联数组。如果改成\"View Data\"会丢失类型信息。您觉得呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Prepare Data Array for View"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "说得对，保留Array吧，技术准确性优先。最后确认一下Send Final Response to Browser，这里Browser要不要改成Client？因为实际可能是API请求，调用方不一定是浏览器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Send Final Response to Browser"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "但前面起点是HTTP Request Received，如果终点写Client，起点也应该对应调整。考虑到这个图主要给Web应用开发者看，Browser更直观。如果是API场景，我们可以另画一个版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP Request Received",
        "Send Final Response to Browser"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同意，保持Browser。那整个图就这样定稿了。请再检查一下所有节点名称的拼写，特别是CodeIgniter、Controller这些容易打错的词。",
      "elements_involved": [
